history.content:
If you’re interested in being a part of the CS 186 course staff for the Fall 2022 semester, please fill out the two forms linked below. Make sure to first log into your Berkeley account. The priority deadline for both applications is Tuesday, May 3rd, 2022, but we’ll review applications submitted after that date on a rolling basis.
  • CS 186 Supplementary Application
    • https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSex6WY0luxcXg9eq6tCzhfQUs-nG-IJClQxzZpYiFTaNR96ZA/viewform
  • Official GSI/Tutor Application
    • https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/gsis/prospective/applications
Best of luck, and we look forward to hearing from you!
Please feel free to email us at cs186@berkeley.edu if you have questions.
